{"tid":1263248,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"十大屋苑反彈　麗港城漲23%最勁","createTime":"2019-06-28T05:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T09:44:38.000Z","uid":110904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c2616373fe180a24986543b964de35664d638ab5","tid":1263248,"uid":110904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190628/20715189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190628%2F20715189&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebfcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=be61f4ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190628%2F20715189&h=938bb552\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190628/20715189</a><br />\n麗港城6月平均呎價升至15,705元 勁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美貿易戰令去年下半年樓市跌入谷底，但很快重拾升軌。綜合代理數字，傳統十大屋苑今年上半年樓價全面反彈，升幅最大的三個屋苑均屬市區樓，其中觀塘麗港城成「反彈王」，樓價半年升23%，緊隨其後是鰂魚涌太古城及康怡花園，分別升22%及18.6%。<br />\n<br />\n過去半年樓市呈V型反彈，以麗港城為例，去年12月平均呎價低見12,738元，本月平均呎價升至15,705元，按月再升7%，半年累漲逾兩成。由於升勢急速，窒礙買家入市步伐，麗港城直至昨日才錄得本月第一宗成交。單位為6座高層C室兩房戶，以812萬元易手，呎價15,705元。而過去半年有兩個屋苑樓價升幅不足一成，為東涌映灣園及紅磡黃埔花園，僅升8.6%及9%。十大屋苑上半年錄近1,300宗成交，其中天水圍嘉湖山莊佔223宗最多，之後是沙田第一城及太古城，分別錄167及163宗。"},{"pid":"5db6baf7647b08c1b2d53fe134dfd2cdf93cf803","tid":1263248,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T09:44:38.000Z","msg":"租樓日日賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}